				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">CHR RAM requires three significant changes to the code and build process: <ul><li>You don't append the CHR to the PRG when building the iNES binary. </li><li>Your code has to .incbin the CHR and copy it to the PPU before displaying anything. </li><li>Animated tiles (e.g. SMB2 quicksand, SMB3 ? blocks) operate differently: you have to copy CHR data during vblank instead of changing a mapper register. </li></ul></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

